    <time_frame>30 days post-transplantation</time_frame>
    <description>Time to initial platelet recovery is defined as 1st of 3 consecutive platelet count measurements tested on different days with a count ≥20 × 10^9/L with no platelet transfusion in the prior 7 days.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
